  "overview": {
    "summary": "Mathew, no last name, is an Astral Elf, Grave Domain Cleric, a mysterious figure who seemingly can control butterflies and heal the sick with ease. His face is covered by these butterflies. He has a gentle and almost ethereal nature, however, not much is known about him. He was found after the main party was captured and held in the prison in Manor Seversova, freed and went alongside them..",
     "personality": "He is seemingly polite, gentle, and ethereal in his actions and words. He is softspoken and calm.",
